aus.family is for discussing Australian family issues and family
life.  There are no off topic conversations as family issues are
wide and varied.  Civility is required, and whilst discussions and
debate are welcome, please keep the tone friendly.

All posts (messages) must be in plain text only and be human-readable.

What is not acceptable:

        - HTML posting
        - Binaries (post a URL instead)
        - Crossposting to more than 3 other newsgroups
        - Commercial advertisements more frequently than one per month
        - For-Sale advertisements
        - Auction advertisements
        - Flaming and ad-hominem attacks
        - Spam and chain letters
